title: NoSleep Podcast S14E16
description:
It’s Episode 16 of Season 14. This week we conjure spells for you about those things which have terrible control over you. “Night of Darkness, Flames of Blood” written by Josh Gauthier (Story starts around 00:05:00) Produced by: Phil Michalski Cast: Narrator – Peter Lewis, Bartender – Dan Zappulla, Partygoer – Mick Wingert, Dancer – Jessica McEvoy, Prospero Quast – Graham Rowat, Cyrilla – Sarah Ruth Thomas “Plastic” written by Austin Gragg (Story starts around 00:25:15) TRIG
